window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>If you can’t take the heat, stay out of the dungeon.</b></p> <p>While most other divers are content to wait out the situation in the safe rooms, Jake and the girls are still trying to find answers as they continue to progress further into the dungeon’s depths, but trouble keeps finding them.</p> <p>Previously unseen and drastically overpowered monsters continue to appear, to the point where even the most battle-hardened dungeon divers need their assistance.</p> <p>There’s also the matter of a certain monster girl with an axe to grind against Jake specifically, but will he be able to survive long enough to see her again?</p> <p><b>We’re in the jungle now, baby. We’re gonna fry.</b></p>"; 
